metadata.name: The tale of motherly affection
metadata.description:
This image occupies a massive part of my heart. 
 
This picture is a natural history moment. Usually, cat moms hold their cubs by scruff. But in this picture, we can see that this mom is carrying her little one in an odd fashion, by one of its leg ! And other cub like why I wasn't get a morning ride like this. Yes,It's a nature history moment. Are you tempted now to look up and down the internet? Yes, you can do that, and to your bewilderment, you will find millions of images of lionesses, tigers, and other big cats and other animals holding their cubs and kittens with neck but not a single pic where they carry by leg.

Artist Name: Tapan Sheth

Edition: 1/1
